<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='131138' id='t-131138'>to drop things off and volunteer.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:23
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='132828' id='t-132828'>MO: Everyone's donating clothing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='134432' id='t-134432'>We should inventory
