</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:30
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='139811' id='t-139811'>MO: Sure. And we need to tell people
what not to bring.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='142417' id='t-142417'>I'll make a Facebook account.
