</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:35
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='144854' id='t-144854'>CO: Yeah, but we don't even know
what houses are accepting help.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='147934' id='t-147934'>We need to canvas and send out volunteers.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:40
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='149963' id='t-149963'>MO: We need to tell people
what not to bring.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='152100' id='t-152100'>Hey, there's a news truck. I'll tell them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='154128' id='t-154128'>CO: You got my number off the news?
