</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:48
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='157176' id='t-157176'>(Together) MO: Insurance won't cover it?
