</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='162852' id='t-162852'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='163877' id='t-163877'>CO: And then the rest of the community
figured out that we had answers.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:58
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='167578' id='t-167578'>MO: I can donate three water heaters,
