</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:02
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='171243' id='t-171243'>CO: My car is in my living room!</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
