<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='185935' id='t-185935'>and now I'm covered in poison ivy.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:18
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='187613' id='t-187613'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:19
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='188736' id='t-188736'>So this is what filled our days.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='190526' id='t-190526'>We had to learn
how to answer questions quickly</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='192764' id='t-192764'>and to solve problems in a minute or less;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='195038' id='t-195038'>otherwise, something
more urgent would come up,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='197262' id='t-197262'>and it wouldn't get done.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:29
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='198620' id='t-198620'>MO: We didn't get our authority
from the board of selectmen</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='201451' id='t-201451'>or the emergency management
director or the United Way.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='204331' id='t-204331'>We just started answering questions
and making decisions</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='206981' id='t-206981'>because someone -- anyone -- had to.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='209640' id='t-209640'>And why not me? I'm a campaign organizer.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='212019' id='t-212019'>I'm good at Facebook.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='213211' id='t-213211'>And there's two of me.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:45
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='214513' id='t-214513'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:47
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='216083' id='t-216083'>CO: The point is, if there's a flood
or a fire or a hurricane,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='219635' id='t-219635'>you, or somebody like you,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='221420' id='t-221420'>are going to step up
and start organizing things.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='224055' id='t-224055'>The other point is that it is hard.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:57
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='226356' id='t-226356'>MO: Lying on the ground
after another 17-hour day,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='229071' id='t-229071'>Caitria and I would empty our pockets</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='230902' id='t-230902'>and try to place dozens of scraps
of paper into context --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='233690' id='t-233690'>all bits of information
