<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='376613' id='t-376613'>Now that expense can be huge,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='378246' id='t-378246'>but if the town can mobilize X amount
of volunteers for Y hours,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='382224' id='t-382224'>the dollar value of that labor used
