<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='387089' id='t-387089'>But who knows that?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='388782' id='t-388782'>Now try to imagine
the sinking feeling you get</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='391028' id='t-391028'>when you've just sent out 2,000 volunteers
