</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:46
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='395622' id='t-395622'>CO: These are three problems
with a common solution.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='398083' id='t-398083'>If we can get the right tools
at the right time</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='401136' id='t-401136'>to the people who will inevitably step up</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='403126' id='t-403126'>and start putting
their communities back together,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='405505' id='t-405505'>we can create new standards
in disaster recovery.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:59
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='408231' id='t-408231'>MO: We needed canvasing tools,
donations databasing,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='411189' id='t-411189'>needs reporting, remote volunteer access,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='414203' id='t-414203'>all in an easy-to-use website.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:07
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='416074' id='t-416074'>CO: And we needed help.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='417535' id='t-417535'>Alvin, our software engineer
