<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='424818' id='t-424818'>And we've been flying into disaster areas
since this past January,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='428334' id='t-428334'>setting up software, training residents</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='430707' id='t-430707'>and licensing the software to areas
