</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:25
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='434969' id='t-434969'>MO: One of our first launches
was after the Dallas tornadoes</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='437819' id='t-437819'>this past April.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='438994' id='t-438994'>We flew into a town
that had a static, outdated website</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='441648' id='t-441648'>and a frenetic Facebook feed,
trying to structure the response,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='444638' id='t-444638'>and we launched our platform.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='446050' id='t-446050'>All of the interest came
in the first four days,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='448316' id='t-448316'>but by the time they lost the news cycle,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='450310' id='t-450310'>that's when the needs came in,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='451771' id='t-451771'>yet they had this massive resource
of what people were able to give</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='454965' id='t-454965'>and they've been able to meet
the needs of their residents.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:48
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='457753' id='t-457753'>CO: So it's working,
but it could be better.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='459833' id='t-459833'>Emergency preparedness is a big deal
