<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='464808' id='t-464808'>Imagine if we could have
these systems ready to go in a place</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='467723' id='t-467723'>before a disaster.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='469972' id='t-469972'>So that's what we're working on.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='471804' id='t-471804'>We're working on getting the software
