<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='475037' id='t-475037'>so people know how to use it</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='476402' id='t-476402'>and so it can be filled ahead of time</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='478208' id='t-478208'>with that micro-information
that drives recovery.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='480614' id='t-480614'>MO: It's not rocket science.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='482471' id='t-482471'>These tools are obvious
