</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:36
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='505089' id='t-505089'>CO: And that makes a difference.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='507203' id='t-507203'>June 1 this year marked the one-year
