<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='511081' id='t-511081'>and our community's never been
more connected or more empowered.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='514398' id='t-514398'>We've been able to see the same
transformation in Texas and in Alabama.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='518654' id='t-518654'>Because it doesn't take Harvard or MIT</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='520501' id='t-520501'>to fly in and fix problems
